title: Mai Dragon
typeOfFood: Chinese, Japanese, Delivery, Take-out, Pan Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese and Chinese food. Has veggies, tofu, and mock meats also. The main menu directions are: choose the style of cooking (such as black bean, chow-mein, general tso's, hunan, kung pao, or sichuan), choose a meat (faux chicken/beef/shripm or vegetables or tofu). Has brown rice. Accept special requests - just let your server know.
